{"tid":2066363,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【突發】印度3名士兵於中印邊境遭解放軍殺死","createTime":"2020-06-16T08:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T10:17:51.000Z","uid":97944,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"5e64995c9f27ab7620271722db4994bdbed883cc","tid":2066363,"uid":97944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/660/cpsprodpb/140AB/production/_112919028_whatsappimage2020-06-16at1.31.33pm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F660%2Fcpsprodpb%2F140AB%2Fproduction%2F_112919028_whatsappimage2020-06-16at1.31.33pm.jpg&h=fdfe8858&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Three Indian soldiers have been killed in a clash with Chinese forces in Ladakh in the disputed Kashmir region.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nThe Indian army said &quot;senior military officials of the two sides are meeting to defuse the situation&quot;, adding that both sides suffered casualties.<br />\n<br />\nChina responded by calling on India not to take unilateral actions or stir up trouble, the Reuters agency reported.<br />\n<br />\nChina has also accused India of crossing the border and attacking Chinese soldiers, the AFP agency said.<br />\n<br />\nChinese foreign ministry spokesman Zhao Lijian was quoted as saying that India had crossed the border, &quot;provoking and attacking Chinese personnel, resulting in serious physical confrontation between border forces on the two sides&quot;.<br />\n<br />\nBeijing has not announced any Chinese casualties.<br />\n<br />\nThe clash comes amid rising tensions between the two countries. India has accused China of sending thousands of troops into Ladakh's Galwan valley.<br />\n<br />\nThe deaths are believed to be the first in decades in a confrontation between the two powers. They have fought only one war so far, in 1962, when India suffered a humiliating defeat.<br />\n<br />\nIndia accuses China of occupying 38,000 sq km of its territory. Several rounds of talks in the last three decades have failed to resolve the boundary disputes.<br />\n<br />\nIn May, dozens of Indian and Chinese soldiers exchanged physical blows in a clash on the border in the northeastern state of Sikkim. And in 2017, the two countries clashed in the region after China tried to extend a border road through a disputed plateau.<br />\n<br />\nThe Indian army is expected to address reporters shortly to provide more information about the incident."},{"pid":"58185f40cd9d83fe33cd7ab61132a10d296ce527","tid":2066363,"uid":97944,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:35:52.000Z","msg":"Source: BBC<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53061476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-53061476&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=09c5650d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-53061476&h=0c001b02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-53061476</a><br />\n<br />\n10分鐘前既新聞"},{"pid":"353dbc5bf1b1b5845ac6052731f5c5b93b47c3dc","tid":2066363,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:36:24.000Z","msg":"開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc67112ac345876ce7013ad9155c27d644eadf7","tid":2066363,"uid":97944,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"353dbc5bf1b1b5845ac6052731f5c5b93b47c3dc","tid":2066363,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:36:24.000Z","msg":"開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"印度好似想縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b67714e028d7c90b8457de3953d8f16a0c0763","tid":2066363,"uid":52264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"c